{"tid":1342832,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有舖頭表示我哋搞到佢冇生意！！","createTime":"2019-07-21T18:00:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-21T18:05:06.000Z","uid":252085,"like":27,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"e5ac451170d620e10c26acc59db71b9a2ad65f6d","tid":1342832,"uid":252085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T18:00:42.000Z","msg":"今日發完夢落佐敦轉車 <br />\n經過吳松街順便去買碗糖水<br />\n等等下有個呀嬸入咗去<br />\n呀嬸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 廢佬老闆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呀嬸：喂枱都唔開 仲以為你冇開檔添<br />\n老闆：今日冇生意呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呀嬸：今日又有嘢搞囉班人 唔知西環定灣仔個邊 搞住晒<br />\n老闆：係呀 班人搞嚟搞去喺到搞搞震阻住晒 俾佢哋搞到我冇晒生意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n聽完我決定以後都唔幫襯！<br />\n幫襯咗幾年覺得間嘢又平幾抵食<br />\n食埋今次我以後都唔撚再食！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">屌你老母明記甜品</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Uwv2skH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUwv2skH.png&h=ce4d4d99&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">就係白色衫呢個廢佬</span><br />\n<br />\n灣仔同西環呢邊關你佐敦閪事咩 <br />\n賴得就賴 同當年啲人乜柒都賴佔中一撚樣<br />\n又唔撚柒見你啲廢佬屌元朗班黑社會暴徒？<br />\n<br />\n我哋搞到你今日冇生意？<br />\n唔淨係今日 你以後都唔撚會有生意呀<br />\n抵制呢間垃圾糖水舖<br />\n去開吳松街廟街個邊嘅手足記住咪撚幫襯<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">明記甜品</span></span>"},{"pid":"9b5e77f97bba77c15ff76fd496d52aa2f9ff81e4","tid":1342832,"uid":264433,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T18:02:27.000Z","msg":"我無野講<br />\n依家係你把口搞到自己無生意啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c73db85e644bbde0863b7461af227290c7d3a8d","tid":1342832,"uid":252085,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T18:03:45.000Z","msg":"記住係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">明記甜品</span></span>呀"},{"pid":"7b39d88246179eddb870cb6eeee723a653b947c6","tid":1342832,"uid":252085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T18:05:06.000Z","msg":"附近有大把糖水舖 唔撚係一定要幫襯你 <br />\n你聽摺埋啦 你啲枱以後都唔撚使擺出嚟㗎喇"}]}